---
title: Roasted Salmon with Burst Cherry Tomatoes & Green Beans
description: We’re roasting rich and flavorful salmon to perfection. Serve it up with our favorite crispy crushed potatoes and garlicky tomatoes and green beans. This dish is bursting with flavor.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54c907626ced6e7c1d8b456a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/54c907626ced6e7c1d8b456a.pdf
